{"question_id": "syn-pdfQA/03_Raw_Question_Answer_Data/research articles/2510.22211v1_rawQA.json#5", "question": "Was the UV spectroscopic observation of Ansky with HST conducted in 2025 and did it confirm that the outburst location is consistent with the galactic center?", "answers": ["Yes"], "prediction": "yes", "raw_answer": "Yes, the UV spectroscopic observation of Ansky with HST was conducted in 2025 and confirmed that the outburst location is consistent with the galactic center. The HST observation was on 2025 May 24 (page 3), and transient astrometry using GALFIT showed an offset of 0.34 ± 0.70 pixels between the barycenter of the PSF and the galaxy center, corresponding to approximately 9 ± 18 pc, indicating consistency with the galactic center (page 3).", "source_hint": "2510.22211v1.pdf", "doc_name": "2510.22211v1.pdf", "category": "syn", "dataset": "03_Raw_Question_Answer_Data", "question_type": "unknown", "evidence_pages": [], "pages": [2, 3, 4, 6, 7, 10], "node_ids": ["2510_22211v1_page4_text_2", "2510_22211v1_page6_text_1", "2510_22211v1_page3_text_5", "2510_22211v1_page2_text_3", "2510_22211v1_page10_figure_0", "2510_22211v1_page6_figure_0", "2510_22211v1_page3_figure_0", "2510_22211v1_page3_text_0", "2510_22211v1_page4_text_0", "2510_22211v1_page3_text_1", "2510_22211v1_page3_text_2", "2510_22211v1_page3_text_3", "2510_22211v1_page3_text_4", "2510_22211v1_page3_text_6", "2510_22211v1_page3_text_7", "2510_22211v1_page4_text_1", "2510_22211v1_page4_text_3", "2510_22211v1_page4_text_4", "2510_22211v1_page4_text_5", "2510_22211v1_page4_text_6", "2510_22211v1_page4_text_7", "2510_22211v1_page10_text_0", "2510_22211v1_page10_text_7", "2510_22211v1_page6_text_0", "keyword::heasoft", "keyword::swift_uvot", "keyword::observation", "keyword::blackbody_model", "2510_22211v1_page3_to_page4_cross_text_0", "2510_22211v1_page3_text_11", "keyword::c_iv_λ1549", "keyword::atlas", "keyword::ztf", "keyword::photometry", "2510_22211v1_page3_text_10", "2510_22211v1_page3_